{"tid":2267703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"天文台伺服器遭黑客入侵 已即時調查事故","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T10:02:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4ecc0542bfa16222d781d17b77118cd1ad13701f","tid":2267703,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"天文台一個供傳媒使用的天氣預報伺服器系統近日遭到入侵，或令有關傳媒機構登入資料外洩，天文台就事件致歉。<br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，近日發現一個傳媒訂閱的天氣預報伺服器系統被不明人士入侵，受影響資料有傳媒機構的登入資訊與一些非敏感天氣資料，天文台已即時調查事故及提出補救措施，包括加強保安系統，亦已為訂閱機構更改密碼。<br />\n<br />\n天文台已就事件通知執法部門，並向各傳媒致歉，由於登入資料或外洩，天文台提醒使用者保持警惕，提防釣魚電郵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/JW2B54TSCFBBFGVWWB46RAXSDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FJW2B54TSCFBBFGVWWB46RAXSDU%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=0768966e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FJW2B54TSCFBBFGVWWB46RAXSDU%2F&h=26ee2589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/JW2B54TSCFBBFGVWWB46RAXSDU/</a>"},{"pid":"0366dc664cc66b51e05891d2e7e2372bd8943d31","tid":2267703,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f780aaeeabbf7281f882a202ea7607ac74da5e","tid":2267703,"uid":264326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"要自制八號波？"},{"pid":"31d8f7aba5a0675b43f2c3ff82802d6ddb864a1b","tid":2267703,"uid":133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"大交合hack撚做咩？想早啲掛8號？"},{"pid":"df18ae9df2ec046449acc4dd5532afd06eec1cd0","tid":2267703,"uid":161684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:23:2